    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents the finest example of its kind. It has been meticulously maintained, with a flawless exterior paint finish and an interior that still looks and smells brand new. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs smoothly with no issues, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in its original, pristine state, making it ideal for a discerning collector or someone seeking a like-new driving experience.",
